title: Mediabridge USB 2.0 - A Male to B Male Cable (6 Feet) - High-Speed with Gold-Plated Connectors - Black
description: Mediabridge 2.0 USB A Male to B Male CableConnect a keyboard, mouse, scanner, hard drive, printer, server, camera & more, to a laptop, computer (Mac/PC) or other USB-enabled device.
